主要翻译
 
tester n (cosmetics, etc.: sample)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 试用品 shì yòng pǐn TC Traditional Chinese 試用品  
 -- The store clerk gave me a tester of face cream.
 
tester n (person who tests)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 测试者 cè shì zhě TC Traditional Chinese 測試者  
 -- Maria is a tester for new exercise equipment.

复合形式： 
 
battery tester n (device: checks power)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 电池测试仪 diàn chí cè shì yí  
 
taste-tester n (who samples food and drink for quality control)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 品尝师，试味员 pǐn cháng shī TC Traditional Chinese 品嚐師  

标题中含有单词 'tester' 的论坛讨论：



I am not a physician , <neither> a camera tester [grammatical?]

Sample Tester

test maker vs tester vs test user

